SAVE YOUR COOKING TIME: Tired of using traditional meat mallet, hammer, pounder? Well, our meat needle tenderizer is here to help you. Save 40% of your time marinating with its ultra sharp blades that can slice even to the toughest meats for more absorbed juicy flavors.

TOP-QUALITY PERFORMANCE: Enjoy easy, hassle-free cooking with our durable 100% Premium Stainless Steel meat tenderizer. It creates tiny channels for quick tenderizing, making any meat juicier and more flavorful whether it's steak or any other meat. Enjoy a tastier & faster meal!

ERGONOMIC ONE-PIECE DESIGN: Unlike competitors, we offer one piece design with non slip handle. No more hassle of detaching or attaching the parts. The blades of our steak tenderizer goes deep into the meat when pressed and automatically retract when no force is applied

EASY TO CLEAN & DISHWASHER SAFE: Gourmet Easy meat tenderizer stainless steel is corrosion, rust-proof & easy to clean. Just soak this one piece with blades for few minutes in warm soapy water and wash it with the brush or simply put it in the dishwasher

BUILT TO LAST: 100% Stainless steel chicken tenderizer (304) crafted for exceptional durability & performance! We at Gourmet Easy use the highest-grade materials and innovative design to ensure that it will last a lifetime! This holiday season, gift our cooking tool and share the joy of delicious meals!
